    <item>
      <title>HPS 投资赢得对破产 DVD 租赁公司 Redbox 的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/hps-investment-fights-for-control-of-bankrupt-dvd-company-redbox</link>
      <description><![CDATA[HPS Investment Partners LLC 赢得了一场法庭斗争，更换了破产的 Redbox Entertainment Inc. 的董事会，并同意为这家 DVD 租赁公司的母公司安排贷款，以便支付员工的工资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/hps-investment-fights-for-control-of-bankrupt-dvd-company-redbox</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:24:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普担忧导致新兴货币跌至两个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/emerging-currencies-decline-in-unison-on-prospects-for-trump-2-0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币周二下跌，因为对特朗普可能在 11 月总统大选中获胜的担忧加剧了对美国国债收益率上升的押注，抵消了美联储主席杰罗姆鲍威尔关于通胀正在重回下行通道的言论的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/emerging-currencies-decline-in-unison-on-prospects-for-trump-2-0</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国债券市场有望进入区间波动，中国人民银行设定收益率下限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/pboc-bond-trading-sets-floor-but-not-cease-market-chase-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，中国央行的发债计划可能会放缓，但不会抑制债券市场的上涨，因为推动债券需求的根本原因不太可能发生逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/pboc-bond-trading-sets-floor-but-not-cease-market-chase-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 07:25:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数收于 5,500 点上方，创下历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着债券收益率下降，华尔街交易员将股市推至历史新高，在杰罗姆·鲍威尔 (Jerome Powell) 指出美国已重回通货紧缩轨道后，交易员开始关注美联储降息的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 22:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
